OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome evening sunshine to start with,
OL,7,Fleading to clear spells. Patchy fog or
OL,8,Ffrost may develop inland overnight,
OL,9,Fwhile low cloud and mist gradually
OL,10,Freturn to the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAny overnight mist or fog
OL,13,Flifting through the morning but
OL,14,Fstaying dry and rather cloudy. A much
OL,15,Fcooler day than Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
