OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and bright spells on Sunday and
OL,7,FMonday with some showery outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain and turning a little warmer
OL,9,Fagain. Mostly dry Tuesday but quite
OL,10,Fcool and cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
